headline: Shopify, Citi named signature picks at Wells Fargo
summary: Investing.com -- Shopify could emerge as an under-the-radar beneficiary of the artificial intelligence boom, according to Wells Fargo, which called the stock its signature pick, raising its price target on the stock to $125 from $107. Brokerage called the Canadian e-commerce firm a “thematic AI story.”
